title: Sun Ra - Artyard in a Box (2012 - 9 albums, 320 bitrate)
description: *9 classic Saturn LP releases from Sun Ra on 7 CDs in an individually numbered box set limited to just 500* All these albums are great, all of them quite different from one another and all featuring a lot of electric keyboards and Moog from the boss. The albums are: Disco 3000, Sleeping Beauty, On Jupiter, Beyond the Purple Star Zone, Oblique Parallax, Horizon, Nidhamu, Dark Myth Equation Visitation The Antique Blacks.
